window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lexi, a human woman on the hunt for a lost friend, never expected to end up in a dragon war. But when her search leads her to a sexy, scorchingly hot Scottish dragon king, Lexi's priorities shift. She's ready to help her newfound, enigmatic lover fight the Dark Fae. But fighting the passion that flares between them will be much harder.... </p> <p>Thorn, the mysterious dragon king with a bad-boy streak, is more than ready to go to war with his enemies. But when a beautiful human woman needs his help - and his strong arms to protect her - Thorn is pulled between fighting with his dragon brothers and giving in to raging desire. </p>"; 
